  <VWE_TacticalGrenades.generalRules.rulesStrings>
    <li>subject->多功能爆炸</li>
    <li>subject_story->为应对每种战斗态势而用手榴弹扩充了军备库</li>
    <li>subject_story->为控制和震慑人群而引入了非致命选项</li>
    <li>subject_story->改良出了能精准定时和起效的引信</li>
    <li>subject_story->为特殊战术需求而调整了装药量</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->用能在所有交战环境中发挥作用的正确工具武装部队</li>
  </VWE_TacticalGrenades.generalRules.rulesStrings>
  
  <!-- EN: trench warfare -->
  <VWE_TrenchWarfare.label>堑壕战</VWE_TrenchWarfare.label>
  <!-- EN: Adapt a trench warfare doctrine with a selection of weapons for close-quarters combat. -->
  <VWE_TrenchWarfare.description>准备好近距战斗装备，推行堑壕战作战方针。</VWE_TrenchWarfare.description>
  <!-- EN:
    <li>subject->entrenched defense</li>
    <li>subject_story->adopted age-old strategies to modern combat, ensuring survival</li>
    <li>subject_story->innovated in close-quarters battle tactics within the trenches</li>
    <li>subject_story->engineered fortifications that blend with the landscape for surprise attacks</li>
